The Smart Campus Event Ticketing & Realtime Event Portal System is a centralized digital platform designed to ensure that students do not miss important university events such as hackathons, workshops, seminars, competitions, and career fairs. In many universities, event information is scattered across different platforms like WhatsApp groups, social media pages, and notice boards, which causes students to remain unaware of valuable opportunities. Our solution is to create a single unified portal where all university events are listed in one place with complete details including date, time, venue, registration deadline, and ticket availability. Students can log in, view upcoming events, register or book tickets, receive notifications, and track their participation. The system will also provide real-time seat availability, digital ticket generation, waitlist management, fraud detection, and administrative control for managing events efficiently. The technology stack for this project includes Supabase (PostgreSQL) for database and authentication, ASP.NET Core (.NET 8) with C# for backend logic, and ASP.NET MVC / Razor Pages with HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap, and JavaScript for the frontend, ensuring a modern, scalable, and secure platform that supports real-time updates and analytics